<div class="container">

<div class="left_container">
<div class="home_title">
RULES:
</div>
<div class="home_content_container">
<ul>
<li>9 players + 1 god</li>
<li>3 mafias, 3 citizens, 1 dacoit, 1 healer, 1 detective</li>
<li>Roles randomnly assigned. Nobody knows who is who expect about self</li>
<li>Objective of mafias is to kill citizens and of citizens is to kill  mafias</li>
<li>Detective and healer support citizens and dacoit support mafias</li>
<li>Mafias can kill at night including self when prompted by god</li>
<li>Healer can heal as well as kill only once during the entire game at night when prompted by god. Healer can kill/heal self</li>
<li>Detective can suspect somebody at night when prompted by god to find out if the suspect is a mafia</li>
<li>During the day dacoit could kill someone he suspects to be a citizen by suicide bombing at any point of the game. However, dacoit too will die</li>
<li>Voting will happen during the day in which mafias objective is to vote out citizens and vice versa for citizens</li>
<li>Voted out persons will be given one chance to explain themselves and again votes will be called</li>
<li>A chat window will be provided for discussions/strategy planning among players</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>

<div class="middle_container">
<div class="middle_game_container">
M<span class="mafia_black">A</span>F<span class="mafia_black">I</span>A
</div>
