<input type="text" name="middle_nick_input" class="middle_nick_input" placeholder="Choose a nickname" />
</div>
<div class="middle_home_start_container centered">
<button name="middle_home_start_button" class="middle_home_start_button slide_up_button"><span>START</span></button>
</div>
<div class="middle_other_container">
<button name="middle_facebook_button" class="slide_up_button middle_facebook_button"><span>Login with Facebook</span></button>
</div>
</div>

<div class="right_container">
<div class="home_title">
GUIDELINES:
</div>
<div class="home_content_container">
<ul>
<li>If you are a mafia you will know other mafias when you are first prompted by god. Use this to your advantage and discuss with other mafias</li>
<li>Discussions in chat window will happen mostly during the day for everybody. Carefully read the arguments of everybody to figure out who is who</li>
<li>Dacoit, if is convinced of somebody being a citizen should kill him by suicide bombing</li>
<li>In case of network disconnects or time delay in player's prompt a default behavior is registered. You can come back to where you left when your network reconnects.</li>
<li>Deception and trickery are key to winning this game. Use them to your advantage</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>

